<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_2344b761-3cd9-4a7c-85dd-b8d353533c3c" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>H4V3</sptc><title id="_8490918e-e844-4d02-82f5-1c4fc41a0ead">Verification of indoor air quality</title><archive-num>2019: V2.4.5</archive-num><subclause id="_b36ca8d2-e9ee-4f7e-8003-394952e6e8da" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_cdc1f7ba-a332-45e1-a377-8ab514338089">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>For a Class 1 building, compliance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1920_3.1.0.xml#_c54cc5a4-d191-493a-84d4-b8e3481924ee" id="_2223aa88-61cf-480a-b974-13b6af1eb781" scope="local" type="subclause">H4P5(1)</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1920_3.1.0.xml#_21d99448-adcb-4fcc-aadc-675aea7372f2" id="_d2fcc74c-fa28-4541-b384-4440c6d1bf69" scope="local" type="subclause">H4P5(2)(a)</xref> is verified when it is determined that the building under typical conditions in use is provided with sufficient ventilation with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1388_0.4.0.xml#_eb74131f-b9dc-42bf-89c2-f68b788f9636" id="_21775c76-94f0-4c4a-9c60-ff6611118db5" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">outdoor air</xref> such that contaminant levels do not exceed the limits specified in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/136_0.5.0.xml#_3c1d26e0-1526-4033-9841-ac95372159c3" id="_c7a843a0-e16e-406a-ba66-ed80